10:17.650 --> 10:21.888 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of electing Republicans to the
House, and
Barry Bennett, a Donald Trump
supporter and

10:21.921 --> 10:23.823 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
