10:23.857 --> 10:25.925 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Gentlemen, thank you both for
joining us.

10:25.959 --> 10:27.794 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mr. Davis, let me start with
you.

10:27.827 --> 10:32.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
