presidential
race is over?

10:39.172 --> 10:41.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOM DAVIS (R), Former U.S.
Congressman: No,
I think he's saying he wants to
make sure

10:41.441 --> 10:44.944 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
