reelected and he
has a working majority.

10:44.978 --> 10:48.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This isn't different than what
he was telling
the House a month ago, which is,
you have

10:48.815 --> 10:50.250 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
