members.

11:01.961 --> 11:06.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when I was campaign chairman
in 2000,
it was actually a similar
arrangement with

11:06.466 --> 11:09.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
