52:05.289 --> 52:06.890 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What will be next year?

52:06.924 --> 52:08.258 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I don't know.

52:08.292 --> 52:10.894 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: None of us really
knows, but we
will be watching.

52:10.928 --> 52:12.830 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg,
